   	<string name="aboutThisAppTitle">About This App</string>
	<string name="aboutThisAppText">
		<b>About this app</b>\n\t
			RelayRemote is an app for controlling an Arduino relay server. The Arduino turns on/off electrical relays when given commands from a client,
			like this app.\n\n
			To use this app, you\'ll need an Arduino and Arduino Ethernet Shield running the sketch found at
			https://github.com/shanet/RelayRemote.\n\n
			More info about setting up Arduino can be found at the link above as can the source code for this app. If you encounter any problems, please
			open an issue on GitHub at the link above.

		\n\n<b>License</b>\n\t
			This application is open source software. It is free to distribute, modify, and use with the exception of it being made closed source and sold for
			commercial purposes without the consent of the author.
	</string>

